\c 17
\s UPawuli utshumayela eThesalonika
\p
\v 1 Kwathi sebedabule iAmfipholi leApoloniya, bafika eThesalonika\x + 17.11,13. 20.4. 27.2. Fil. 4.16. 1 Thes. 1.1. 2 Thes. 1.1. 2 Tim. 4.10.\x*, lapho okwakukhona isinagoge lamaJuda;
\v 2 njalo njengomkhuba kaPawuli wangena kuwo\x + 17.10. 13.14. Mat. 4.23.\x*, wakhulumisana lawo \add ngo\add*kuvela emibhalweni\x + 8.35. 18.28. 28.23. Mat. 26.24.\x* okwamasabatha amathathu,
\v 3 evula etshengisa\x + Luka 24.32.\x* ukuthi kwakufanele uKristu ahlupheke avuke kwabafileyo\x + 3.18.\x*, lokuthi: UJesu lo\x + 18.5,28.\x*, mina engimtshumayela kini, unguKristu.
\v 4 Labanye babo bakholwa, bazihlanganisa loPawuli\x + 28.24.\x* loSilasi\x + 15.34.\x*, njalo ixuku elikhulu lamaGriki\x + Joha. 12.20.\x* akhonzayo\x + 17.17. 13.43.\x*, lakwabesifazana abadumileyo abangabalutshwana\x + Mark. 6.21.\x*.
\v 5 Kodwa amaJuda angakholwayo\x + 14.2.\x* aba lomona\x + 7.9. 5.17.\x*, athatha amanye amadoda amabi angamavila emdangeni, enza ixuku, adunga umuzi\x + Hlu. 9.4.\x*; ahlasela indlu kaJasoni\x + Roma 16.21.\x*, edinga ukubakhuphela ebantwini;
\v 6 kwathi engabatholi, adonsela uJasoni labazalwane abathile kubaphathi bomuzi\x + 17.10,14. Joha. 21.23.\x*, ememeza \add esithi\add*: Laba\x + 16.20.\x* abayaluzelisa\x + 21.38. Gal. 5.12. Seb. 24.5.\x* umhlaba, bona sebefikile lalapha\x + 17.31. Mat. 24.14.\x*,
\v 7 uJasoni abemukeleyo\x + Luka 10.38.\x*; lalaba bonke benza okuphambene lemithetho kaKesari\x + Luka 2.1.\x*, besithi kukhona enye inkosi, \add eng\add*uJesu\x + Luka 23.2. Joha. 18.33,36,37. 19.12.\x*.
\v 8 Asedunga ixuku labaphathi bomuzi besizwa lezizinto.
\v 9 Kwathi sebethethe isibambiso kuJasoni lakwabanye, abakhulula.
\s UPawuli utshumayela eBeriya
\p
\v 10 Njalo abazalwane\x + 17.10,14. Joha. 21.23.\x* bahle basusa uPawuli\x + 9.25. 17.14. Mat. 10.23.\x* loSilasi babathuma eBeriya ebusuku\x + 15.34.\x*; okwathi sebefikile khona basuka baya esinagogeni lamaJuda\x + 17.10. 13.14. Mat. 4.23.\x*.
\v 11 Lawo ayelungile kulalawo aweThesalonika\x + 17.11,13. 20.4. 27.2. Fil. 4.16. 1 Thes. 1.1. 2 Thes. 1.1. 2 Tim. 4.10.\x*, emukela ilizwi ngokuvuma konke, ehlolisisa imibhalo\x + Luka 16.29.\x* insuku ngensuku, ukuthi zinjalo yini lezizinto\x + Luka 11.3.\x*.
\v 12 Ngakho amanengi kuwo akholwa, lakwabesifazana abahloniphekayo abangamaGriki lakwabesilisa abangabalutshwana\x + 13.50. Mark. 15.43.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa kwathi amaJuda eThesalonika esekwazi ukuthi ilizwi likaNkulunkulu liyatshunyayelwa nguPawuli leBeriya\x + 17.10. 20.4.\x*, eza lakhona enyakazelisa amaxuku.
\v 14 Njalo ngalesosikhathi abazalwane bahle bamthuma uPawuli kungathi uya elwandle\x + 17.10.\x*; kodwa uSilasi\x + 15.34.\x* loTimothi\x + 16.1.\x* basala khona.
\v 15 Lalabo ababephelekezela uPawuli\x + 15.3.\x*, bamfikisa eAtene\x + 18.1. 1 Thes. 3.1.\x*; sebemukele umlayezelo\x + 18.5.\x* oya kuSilasi\x + 15.34.\x* loTimothi, ukuthi beze kuye ngokuphangisa okukhulu, basuka bahamba\x + 16.1.\x*.
\s UPawuli utshumayela eAtene
\p
\v 16 Kwathi uPawuli esabalindele eAtene, umoya wakhe wakhathazeka phakathi kwakhe, ebona umuzi ugcwele izithombe\x + 17.15.\x*.
\v 17 Ngakho waphikisana\x + 17.2. 18.4,19. 19.8,9. 24.12.\x* lamaJuda esinagogeni\x + 17.2,10.\x* labanye abakhonzayo\x + 17.4.\x*, lasemdangeni insuku zonke lalabo ahlangana labo.
\v 18 Labathile kuzo izazi zamaEpikuri lamaStoyiki baphikisana laye. Labanye bathi: Uwumane\f + \fk uwumane: \fl kumbe, \fq umuntu ophansi.\f* lolu lufuna ukuthini? Kodwa abanye \add bathi\add*: Kungathi ungotshumayela onkulunkulu bezizweni; ngoba ngevangeli watshumayela kubo uJesu\x + 5.42.\x* lokuvuka \add kwabafileyo\x + 4.2.\x*\add*.
\v 19 Basebemthatha, bamusa eAreyopagu besithi: Singazi yini ukuthi iyini limfundiso entsha oyifundisayo?
\v 20 Ngoba uletha indaba ezimangalisayo ezithile endlebeni zethu; ngakho sifisa ukwazi ukuthi lezizinto ziyini.
\v 21 Ngoba bonke abeAtene lezethekeli ezihlala khona babechitha isikhathi kungeyisikho ngolutho olunye, ngaphandle kokutshela lokuzwa into entsha\x + 2.10.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Kwathi uPawuli esima phakathi kweAreyopagu, wathi: Madoda maAtene, ngiyabona ukuthi ezintweni zonke kungathi lilenkolelo enkulu\x + 25.19.\x*.
\v 23 Ngoba ngithe ngidabula ngikhangela izinto zenu elizikhonzayo, ngasengifica ilathi elilotshwe \add ukuthi\add*: KUNKULUNKULU ONGAZIWAYO\x + Mat. 22.20.\x*. Lowo-ke elimkhonza lingamazi, nguye mina engimtshumayela kini\x + 17.3.\x*.
\v 24 UNkulunkulu owenza umhlaba lakho konke okukuwo\x + 14.15.\x*, yena, oyiNkosi yezulu lomhlaba\x + Mat. 11.25.\x*, kahlali emathempelini\x + 7.48.\x* enziwe ngezandla\x + Mark. 14.58.\x*,
\v 25 futhi kakhonzwa ngezandla zabantu, \add njengo\add*swela ulutho\x + Hlab. 50.8-12.\x*, ngoba yena uqobo lwakhe uyabapha bonke impilo lokuphefumula lazo zonke izinto\x + Gen. 2.7. Nani 16.22. Jobe 27.3.\x*;
\v 26 njalo wazenza zonke izizwe zabantu zivela egazini linye, ukuthi zihlale ebusweni bonke bomhlaba, wazimisela izikhathi eziqunyiweyo ngaphambili\x + 17.31. Luka 22.22.\x* lemingcele yokuhlala kwazo\x + Dute. 32.8.\x*;
\v 27 ukuze zidinge iNkosi, ukuthi mhlawumbe sibili zimuzwe zi\add m\add*thole, njalo kanti kakhatshana kulowo lalowo wethu\x + 14.17.\x*.
\v 28 Ngoba kuye siphila njalo sihamba futhi sikhona\x + Jobe 12.10.\x*; njengoba lembongi ezithile zakini zithe: Ngoba futhi siyinzalo yakhe\x + Tit. 1.12. 1 Kor. 15.32.\x*.
\v 29 Ngakho lokhu siyinzalo kaNkulunkulu, kakufanele ukuthi sinakane ukuthi ubuNkulunkulu bunjengegolide kumbe isiliva loba ilitshe, okubazwe ngeminwe langokunakana kwabantu\x + Isa. 40.18,25. 46.5.\x*.
\v 30 Ngakho izikhathi zokungazi uNkulunkulu kazinanzanga\x + 1 Pet. 1.14. Seb. 14.16.\x*, kodwa khathesi uyalaya bonke abantu endaweni zonke ukuthi baphenduke\x + Luka 24.47. Tit. 2.11,12. 1 Pet. 4.3.\x*;
\v 31 ngoba umisile usuku, azakwahlulela\x + Joha. 5.22. Seb. 10.42. Roma 2.16. Seb. 24.25. Roma 14.10. 2 Kor. 5.10.\x* ngalo umhlaba ngokulunga\x + 17.6.\x*, ngendoda ayimisileyo\x + 17.31. Luka 22.22.\x*, waqinisa\f + \fk waqinisa: \fl kumbe, \fq wapha ukholo.\f* kubo bonke, ngokuyivusa kwabafileyo\x + 2.24. Joha. 16.10,11.\x*.
\v 32 Kwathi besizwa ngokuvuka kwabafileyo\x + 17.31,18.\x*, abanye bahleka usulu; kodwa abanye bathi: Sizaphinda sikuzwe ngalokhu\x + 24.25.\x*.
\v 33 Langokunjalo uPawuli waphuma phakathi kwabo.
\v 34 Kodwa amadoda athile anamathela kuye, akholwa; phakathi kwawo kwakukhona loDiyonisiyu umAreyopagu\x + 17.19,22.\x*, lowesifazana obizo lakhe nguDamari, labanye kanye labo.